name: Slackjaw - Fremantle's Finest
description:
After many years representing Perth in battles, open mic events and sharing the stage with some of the finest artists this country has to offer, Slackjaw has come forth to release his debut album “Fremantles Finest”.

The album is 12 tracks deep and features production from Rob Shaker, Hykus & Episode. The releases biggest drawcard is its lyrical and musical diversity, from straight up boom-bap bangers to party jams and more personal and reflective numbers giving the listener a dose of Slackjaw’s personality.

1) Timeless
2) Make It Plain
3) TCB
4) You & I
5) Perth City
6) Showin Love
7) Take It Slow
8) Somethin Breezy
9) In Your Speakers
10) Rain's Dope
11) Hearing Voices
12) Showin Love 2

All tracks recorded @ Extended Play by Episode except "In Your Speakers" recorded at Rob Shakers studio by Rob Shaker & "Perth City" recorded by Episode @ Episode's Crib. All tracks mixed by Hykus except "Timeless", "You And I" and "TCB" mixed by Dazastah and "Perth City" mixed by Episode.
All cuts performed by Rob Shaker
Mastered by Joe Carra @ Crystal Mastering
Art Direction: Aaron Puls

Tracks 1, 3, 6, 9, and 11 Produced by Rob Shaker
Tracks 2, 4 and 10 Produced by Hykus
Tracks 5, 7, 8 and 12 Produced by Episode
